Subject: CHANGE: add an integer divide to LPN expression syntax
Date: Sat, 12 Jun 2010 16:31:38 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

Add an integer divide function to the LPN expression syntax.   
Currently, atacs considers "/" as integer divide but LEMA considers it  
as floating point divide.  It should be made to be consistently  
floating point divide with a new function "idiv" which does integer  
divide.

